> +
> +config NO_IDLE_HZ
> +       bool
> +       depends on PARAVIRT
> +       default y
> +       help
> +         Switches the regular HZ timer off when the system is going
> idle.
> +         This helps a hypervisor detect that the Linux system is
> idle,
> +         reducing the overhead of idle systems. 
